# CDS Modeling

Read the **CDS Modeling** and **Service Definitions** sections of `docs/ai/cap-coding-standards.md`.

## Quick Reference

- Use `cuid`, `managed` from `@sap/cds/common` on all entities
- Use `Association` for references, `Composition` for owned children
- Use `@title` / `@description` for metadata instead of verbose OData annotations
- Use code lists (`sap.common.CodeList`) for status/type enumerations
- Keep `@UI.*` annotations in `app/<appname>/annotations.cds`, not here
- Use CDS MCP `search_docs` when unsure about annotation syntax or CDS features
